'''Brett Weston''' (, —, ) was an American photographer and the second son of photographer .  Brett’s photographs often approach abstraction, with subjects that are difficult to decipher.  He is best known for his work in the dunes around Oceano, California, a subject that he shared with his father Edward Weston.   
